layout.house_prompt: This cozy bedroom features a full-size bed against a wall with two nightstands on each side where the left one has a small clock. A small desk sits in the corner with a comfortable chair for studying or working. Opposite the bed, a spacious dresser provides additional storage. Adjacent to the bedroom, the living room has a recliner and an ottoman facing a low coffee table with a small vase and magazines. A large bookshelf in the corner holds books and board games, while a wide couch provides space for gatherings. Just off the living room, a small gaming room with a gaming console and two beanbag chairs offers a dedicated space for entertainment, complete with a small shelf for controllers and headsets.

hallway.text_description: A cozy, simple entry vestibule/foyer that buffers the living room for privacy and wind control; minimal decor, no extra furniture specified.

living_room.text_description: A cozy living room with a recliner and an ottoman facing a low coffee table holding a small vase and magazines, a wide couch for gatherings, and a large corner bookshelf filled with books and board games.

bedroom.text_description: A cozy bedroom featuring a full-size bed against a wall with two nightstands on each side (left nightstand has a small clock), a small desk in the corner with a comfortable chair for studying or working, and a spacious dresser opposite the bed.

gaming_room.text_description: A cozy gaming room just off the living room with a gaming console setup, two beanbag chairs, and a small shelf for controllers and headsets.
